name: Nacho Jump
description:
This game was made for the Trijam #111

It's the first game I've ever finished. And this inside a 3-hour game jam!

Nacho Jump

You are a Nacho who's trying to become the master of the Nacho Jump.

(It's a very real sport inside the Nacho Community :D)

Can you get 5000 Points?

For my part, I wasn't able to.

Good Luck!!
